metadata.name: Sugarcane Membership Pass
metadata.description:
There are only 500 Sugarcane Membership Passes and represent your early access to experience our Society’s Journey to create Sir Byron’s Private Reserve, the finest collection of Rare Rum Barrels and Rare Human Minds the world has ever seen.

But more than that, indicates the very crucial fact that you believed in us since year 0, when [Rare Spirits Society](https://www.rarespirits.io/) was just a big hairy audacious idea. Being a Sugarcane holder means you will always get that extra something special, so hold them dearly.

Go on and smash your day, shoulders back!
